rows.label: bf03300100_0020
rows.name:
It's a distribution center. The government tries
to ration out what little resources they have.

rows.label: bf03300100_0030
rows.name: In practice, it's just first come, first served.

rows.label: bf03300100_0050
rows.name: Okay. That's the last one for today.

rows.label: bf03300100_0070
rows.name:
Come on! I'm a soldier! 
Been busting my gut for this country!

rows.label: bf03300100_0080
rows.name:
That should be going to me.
Not the likes of you!

rows.label: bf03300100_0090
rows.name:
Uh? Don't look at me like that!
Respect your elders, you snot-nosed brat!

rows.label: bf03300100_0110
rows.name:
What do you think you're doing?
She's just a child!

rows.label: bf03300100_0130
rows.name: H-huh? Who the hell are you?

rows.label: bf03300100_0140
rows.name: Rex... This isn't our business. Leave it!

rows.label: bf03300100_0150
rows.name:
Being an adult isn't just about barking orders.
Sometimes you need to help someone weaker!

rows.label: bf03300100_0160
rows.name:
Shut your face!
You don't know what the hell you're talking about!
